list.name: Test start
list.query: SELECT title, text, tags FROM "ios.annotations" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "title" =~ /.*STARTED/ AND space =~ /^$space$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND label =~ /^$label$/ AND iosVersion =~ /^$iosVersion$/ AND deviceModel =~ /^$deviceModel$/ AND device =~ /^$device$/

list.name: Test finished
list.query: SELECT title, text, tags FROM "ios.annotations" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "title" =~ /.*FINISHED/ AND space =~ /^$space$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND label =~ /^$label$/ AND iosVersion =~ /^$iosVersion$/ AND deviceModel =~ /^$deviceModel$/ AND device =~ /^$device$/

list.name: Events
list.query: SELECT text,timestampText FROM "ios.annotations" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "title" !='[ Test STARTED ]' AND "title" !='[ Test FINISHED ]' AND space =~ /^$space$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND label =~ /^$label$/ AND iosVersion =~ /^$iosVersion$/ AND deviceModel =~ /^$deviceModel$/ AND device =~ /^$device$/ AND "text" =~ /.*$event.*/

list.name: ComplexEvents
list.query: SELECT text,timestampText FROM "ios.annotations" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "title" !='[ Test STARTED ]' AND "title" !='[ Test FINISHED ]' AND space =~ /^$space$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND label =~ /^$label$/ AND iosVersion =~ /^$iosVersion$/ AND deviceModel =~ /^$deviceModel$/ AND device =~ /^$device$/ AND "text" =~ /.*$complexEvent.*/
